og prostora","Savremeni kontroleri i NAND čelije","Korisnici dobivaju stvarni kapacitet"],"source":{"name":"XDA Developers","url":"https://www.xda-developers.com/stop-wasting-your-modern-ssd-on-over-provisioning/"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/your-ssds-10-tax-is-deadheres-why-you-should-kill-/main.jpg","alt":"Zaboravite na 10% rezervu za SSD, 2026. je tu"},"subtitle":"Stvarni kapacitet se konačno podudara s onim na naljepnici","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/your-ssds-10-tax-is-deadheres-why-you-should-kill-/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Stvarni kapacitet se konačno podudara s onim na naljepnici"},"tags":["SSD","Storage Capacity","Hardware"],"geo":{"name":"Seoul, South Korea","lat":37.5665,"lon":126.978,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$7","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-24-gps-jamming-surge-leaves-1-100-ships-stranded-in-t","dbId":652,"title":"GPS napadi na Bliskom Istoku: 1.100 brodova u krizi","category":"technology","date":"2026-03-24T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-24T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Kada satelitska navigacija prestane biti pouzdana, ne radi se samo o kartografskoj grešci.","execSummary":"The article dissects the practical fallout of GPS spoofing attacks on 1,100+ ships in the Middle East, linking them to the US-Israel strike on Iran. It focuses on real-world disruptions (delays, insurance costs, operational chaos) and the market’s scramble for alternatives—highlighting how a once-reliable utility (GPS) is now a vulnerability requiring costly backups.","keyPoints":["1.100 brodova pogođeno GPS ometanjima u dva mjeseca","Veza s američko-izraelskim napadom na Iran 28. veljače","Navigacijski sustavi postali nova meta hibridnog ratovanja"],"source":{"name":"Wired","url":"https://www.wired.com/story/gps-attacks-on-ships-spike-amid-the-us-and-israeli-war-on-iran/"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/gps-jamming-surge-leaves-1-100-ships-stranded-in-t/main.jpg","alt":"GPS napadi na Bliskom Istoku: 1.100 brodova u krizi"},"subtitle":"Razmještanje lažnih signala nije više teorija — realni troškovi za globalnu logistiku","tags":["GPS Spoofing","Maritime Logistics","Cybersecurity Threats","Global Navigation"],"geo":{"name":"Global","lat":0,"lon":0,"countryCode":"XX"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$8","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-23-quic-in-proxy-mode-cloudflares-2x-speedup-isnt-jus","dbId":638,"title":"QUIC u Proxy Modu: Cloudflare ubrzava SASE za 2x","category":"technology","date":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Part 1: Kada cloudflare objavi da je prepisao dio svoje SASE arhitekture, obično to znači da će netko drugi morati pratiti.","execSummary":"Cloudflare’s shift to QUIC in Proxy Mode doubles throughput and cuts latency, but the real story is whether this forces the SASE market to compete on measurable performance—not just security. For users, it means faster cloud apps if their infrastructure supports it; for competitors, it’s a wake-up call to stop hiding behind vague ‘holistic’ claims.","keyPoints":["QUIC zamjenjuje TCP u Proxy Modu — bez overheada","2x veći throughput, manja kašnjenja za korisnike","SASE tržište pod pritiskom: tko prati, tko ostaje iza"],"source":{"name":"","url":"https://blog.cloudflare.com/faster-sase-proxy-mode-quic/"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/quic-in-proxy-mode-cloudflares-2x-speedup-isnt-jus/main.jpg","alt":"QUIC u Proxy Modu: Cloudflare ubrzava SASE za 2x"},"subtitle":"Realna prednost ili samo benchmark trik — što korisnici osjećaju u praksi","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/quic-in-proxy-mode-cloudflares-2x-speedup-isnt-jus/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Realna prednost ili samo benchmark trik — što korisnici osjećaju u praksi"},"tags":["Cloudflare","SASE","QUIC Protocol"],"geo":{"name":"San Francisco, United States","lat":37.7749,"lon":-122.4194,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$9","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-23-ciscos-cvss-10-0-flaws-a-firewall-fail-with-real-c","dbId":637,"title":"Cisco otkriva kritične rupe: kontrolirajte cijele sustave","category":"technology","date":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Kada Cisco objavi sigurnosno ažuriranje s 48 zakrpa za 25 različitih ranjivosti, to bi trebalo biti znak da sustav radi.","execSummary":"Cisco's March 2026 security bundle patches 48 flaws, including two CVSS 10.0 vulnerabilities in Secure FMC, exposing a tension between routine updates and existential trust in network security infrastructure. The real test isn’t the patches themselves but whether users—especially SMBs—will implement them before exploits emerge, and what this means for Cisco’s dominance in a market where Palo Alto and Fortinet are ready to capitalize on doubts.","keyPoints":["Dvije CVSS 10.0 rane u Secure FMC – potpuna kontrola za napadače","48 zakrpa u jednom paketu: koliko će korisnika zapravo ažurirati?","Cisco gubi povjerenje ili samo obavlja posao?"],"source":{"name":"","url":"https://www.notebookcheck.net/Cisco-admits-total-security-failure-Critical-flaws-give-hackers-complete-control.1243546.0.html"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/ciscos-cvss-10-0-flaws-a-firewall-fail-with-real-c/main.jpg","alt":"Cisco otkriva kritične rupe: kontrolirajte cijele sustave"},"subtitle":"Ažuriranje koje bi trebalo biti rutina postaje alarm za cijele mrežne ekosustave","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/ciscos-cvss-10-0-flaws-a-firewall-fail-with-real-c/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Ažuriranje koje bi trebalo biti rutina postaje alarm za cijele mrežne ekosustave"},"tags":["Cisco","Cybersecurity","Network Infrastructure","Vulnerability Management"],"geo":{"name":"San Jose, United States","lat":37.338208,"lon":-121.886329,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$a","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-23-byds-1-500kw-charger-speed-isnt-the-real-story","dbId":636,"title":"BYD 'flash charger' ruši američku granicu brzine punjenja","category":"technology","date":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"BYD-ov najnoviji 'flash charger' od 1500kW nije samo još jedan tehnički podatak.","execSummary":"BYD's launch of a 1500kW EV charger, over three times faster than the current US maximum, is a direct challenge to global charging infrastructure, shifting competition from vehicle range to charging speed. Its planned expansion outside China forces other players to adapt, but real-world adoption hinges on grid capacity, battery compatibility, and cost, making it a pivotal moment for the entire EV ecosystem.","keyPoints":["Stanka od 1500kW za dvije vozila istovremeno","Plan za izvan kinesku ekspanziju","Utjecaj na cijeli EV ekosustav"],"source":{"name":"","url":"https://electrek.co/2026/03/05/byds-new-1500kw-flash-charger-is-over-3x-faster-than-anything-us-has/"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/byds-1-500kw-charger-speed-isnt-the-real-story/main.jpg","alt":"BYD 'flash charger' ruši američku granicu brzine punjenja"},"subtitle":"Stvarna cijena ovog napretka","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/byds-1-500kw-charger-speed-isnt-the-real-story/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Stvarna cijena ovog napretka"},"tags":["BYD","Electric Vehicle Charging","Fast Charging Technology"],"geo":{"name":"Shenzhen, Kina","lat":22.5431,"lon":114.0579,"countryCode":"XX"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$b","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-23-lifis-10gbps-promise-collides-with-realitys-walls","dbId":635,"title":"LiFi od 10 Gbps: brži, jeftiniji – ali ne radi kroz zidove","category":"technology","date":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Ako vam je ikad smetalo da Wi-Fi signal slabi kroz debele zidove ili da vam susjed krade propusnost, [pureLiFi](https://purelifi.","execSummary":"PureLiFi’s 10Gbps LiFi promises plug-and-play speeds but collides with a fundamental flaw: line-of-sight dependency. This analysis dissects the gap between lab-grade specs and real-world usability, questioning whether the trade-offs (no walls, no movement) justify the performance for mainstream users or businesses.","keyPoints":["10 Gbps bežično, ali samo s direktnom vidljivošću","Plug-and-play instalacija za uredske mreže","Cijena niža od Taarinog rješenja, ali s velikim ograničenjem"],"source":{"name":"","url":"https://www.techradar.com/pro/taaras-rival-promises-10gbps-wireless-internet-with-a-seemingly-cheaper-plug-and-play-setup-but-theres-a-big-elephant-in-the-room"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/lifis-10gbps-promise-collides-with-realitys-walls/main.png","alt":"LiFi od 10 Gbps: brži, jeftiniji – ali ne radi kroz zidove"},"subtitle":"Teorijski napredak koji se sudara s osnovnom fizikom prostora","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/lifis-10gbps-promise-collides-with-realitys-walls/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Teorijski napredak koji se sudara s osnovnom fizikom prostora"},"tags":["LiFi","Wireless Communication","High-Speed Networking"],"geo":{"name":"Edinburgh, United Kingdom","lat":55.9533,"lon":-3.1883,"countryCode":"GB"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$c","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-23-intel-s-arrow-lake-refresh-forces-amd-to-sweat","dbId":630,"title":"Intel se vraća: Arrow Lake Refresh stisnuo AMD-u grlo","category":"technology","date":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Intel je napokon stavio prst na bolnu točku tržišta: **cijenu i performanse bez kompromisa**.","execSummary":"Intel's Arrow Lake Refresh (270K Plus/250K Plus) directly challenges AMD's Ryzen 9000 dominance with aggressive pricing ($199–$299) and near-flagship performance. The real tension isn’t specs but ecosystem costs (motherboard availability) and whether Intel can sustain this momentum beyond initial hype. Users gain leverage; AMD faces its first serious pricing pressure in years.","keyPoints":["270K Plus i 250K Plus: Intelove cijenovne bombe za 299 i 199 dolara","Zen 5 dominacija u pitanju – AMD prvi put pod pritiskom","Stvarni performansi vs. marketing: tko stvarno osjeća razliku"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/intel-s-arrow-lake-refresh-forces-amd-to-sweat/main.jpg","alt":"Intel se vraća: Arrow Lake Refresh stisnuo AMD-u grlo"},"subtitle":"Dvije nove CPU opcije koje mijenjaju pravila – ali ne za sve korisnike.","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/intel-s-arrow-lake-refresh-forces-amd-to-sweat/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Dvije nove CPU opcije koje mijenjaju pravila – ali ne za sve korisnike."},"tags":["Intel","Arrow Lake Refresh","CPU","AMD","Hardware"],"geo":{"name":"San Francisco, US","lat":37.7749,"lon":-122.4194,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$d","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-23-grapheneos-defies-age-laws-privacy-at-what-cost","title":"GrapheneOS odbio zakon o dobi: što znači za privatnost?","category":"technology","date":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Kada GrapheneOS, android fork usmjeren na ekstremnu privatnost, javno odbije nove zakone o provjeri dobi kod postavljanja uređaja, to nije samo korporativna pobuna — to je test granica između regulacije i korisničkih prava.","execSummary":"GrapheneOS's refusal to comply with age verification laws isn’t just defiance—it’s a litmus test for whether privacy can remain non-negotiable in consumer tech. The move exposes a growing divide: systems that adapt to regulation (and surveillance) vs. those that reject it, risking marginalization but offering true user control. Watch for ecosystem fragmentation and whether mainstream users will tolerate friction for privacy.","keyPoints":["GrapheneOS neće tražiti osobne podatke ni za provjeru dobi","Zakoni o dobi na meti: tko još riskira odbijanjem?","Android fork dokazuje: privatnost može biti nepregovorna"],"source":{"name":"Tom's Hardware","url":"https://www.tomshardware.com/software/operating-systems/grapheneos-refuses-to-comply-with-age-verification-laws"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/grapheneos-defies-age-laws-privacy-at-what-cost/main.jpg","alt":"GrapheneOS odbio zakon o dobi: što znači za privatnost?"},"subtitle":"Kada operativni sustav kaže 'ne' regulaciji — tko zapravo gubi?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/grapheneos-defies-age-laws-privacy-at-what-cost/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Kada operativni sustav kaže 'ne' regulaciji — tko zapravo gubi?"},"tags":["GrapheneOS","Privacy","Regulation"],"geo":{"name":"Mountain View, CA","lat":37.3861,"lon":-122.0839,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$e","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-22-body-heat-to-power-seoul-researchers-crack-battery","title":"Pametni satovi bez baterije? Toplina tijela postaje struja","category":"technology","date":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Ako vam je dosadilo mijenjati baterije na pametnom satu svake dvije godine – ili još gore, kada vam uređaj umre usred trčanja – istraživači s Seoulskog nacionalnog sveučilišta možda imaju rješenje.","execSummary":"Seoul National University's flat, heat-powered energy film challenges battery dependency in wearables—focus shifts to real-world efficiency and cost trade-offs for smartwatches and health monitors. The angle: practical adoption barriers vs. marketing promises, with ecosystem effects on low-power device design.","keyPoints":["Tanki filmovi pretvaraju toplinu tijela u električnu energiju","Prvi potpuno ravni izvor napajanja za nosive uređaje","Potencijalno rješenje za baterije u pametnoj odjeći i medicini"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/body-heat-to-power-seoul-researchers-crack-battery/main.jpg","alt":"Pametni satovi bez baterije? Toplina tijela postaje struja"},"subtitle":"Što se stvarno mijenja za korisnike i proizvođače","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/body-heat-to-power-seoul-researchers-crack-battery/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Što se stvarno mijenja za korisnike i proizvođače"},"tags":["Body Heat Harvesting","Thermoelectric Energy","Batteryless Devices"],"geo":{"name":"Seoul, South Korea","lat":37.5665,"lon":126.978,"countryCode":"KR"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$f","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-22-byds-5-minute-ev-charge-fast-but-wheres-the-catch","title":"BYD-ova ‘munja-baterija’ puni se za 5 minuta. Ali ima presjeka","category":"technology","date":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Ako vam je dosadilo čekanje ispred punjača dok se baterija vašeg električnog auta sporo napunjava, BYD je upravo postavio novi benchmark: **Blade Battery 2.","execSummary":"BYD’s Blade Battery 2.0 promises 5-minute charging at 1.5 MW, but the real story isn’t the spec sheet—it’s the infrastructure gap and who pays to close it. For fleets, this could be transformative; for everyday drivers, it’s a premium feature with limited real-world benefit until charging networks catch up.","keyPoints":["Blade Battery 2.0 podnosi 1,5 MW — to je 10x više od prosjeka","5 minuta punjenja: koliko je to realno za vozače?","Infrastruktura ostaje slabo mjesto: tko će platiti nadogradnju?"],"source":{"name":"TechCrunch","url":"https://techcrunch.com/2026/03/05/byd-rolls-out-ev-batteries-with-5-minute-flash-charging-but-theres-a-catch/"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/byds-5-minute-ev-charge-fast-but-wheres-the-catch/main.jpg","alt":"BYD-ova ‘munja-baterija’ puni se za 5 minuta. Ali ima presjeka"},"subtitle":"1,5 megavata snage zvuči impresivno. Ali koliko to stvarno znači za vas i vaš dnevni ritam?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/byds-5-minute-ev-charge-fast-but-wheres-the-catch/subtitle.jpg","alt":"1,5 megavata snage zvuči impresivno. Ali koliko to stvarno znači za vas i vaš dnevni ritam?"},"tags":["BYD","Electric Vehicle Battery","Fast Charging Technology"],"geo":{"name":"San Francisco, US","lat":37.7749,"lon":-122.4194,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$10","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-22-everest-ai-promises-speed-but-what-about-substance","title":"Everest AI: Brzina koja mijenja pravila igre u IPMI-u","category":"technology","date":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Everest AI, najnoviji proizvod koji se pojavio na Product Huntu, obećava da će biti 'najbrži IPMI single board računar na svijetu'.","execSummary":"Everest AI claims to be the world's fastest IPMI single board computer, potentially disrupting the embedded computing market by offering lower latency and operational costs. However, its real impact hinges on reliability, scalability, and adoption in enterprise environments rather than just raw speed.","keyPoints":["Najbrži IPMI single board računar do sada","Potencijalno sniženje troškova server infrastrukture","Nepoznato koliko će biti dostupno korisnicima"],"source":{"name":"Product Hunt","url":"https://www.producthunt.com/products/everest-ai"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/everest-ai-promises-speed-but-what-about-substance/main.jpg","alt":"Everest AI: Brzina koja mijenja pravila igre u IPMI-u"},"subtitle":"Što se stvarno promijenilo u svijetu embedded računarstva?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/everest-ai-promises-speed-but-what-about-substance/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Što se stvarno promijenilo u svijetu embedded računarstva?"},"tags":["Everest AI","Embedded Computing","IPMI"],"geo":{"name":"Santa Clara, CA","lat":37.3875,"lon":-122.0575,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$11","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-22-fbis-surveillance-hack-more-than-just-a-security-s","title":"FBI-ov hack: Koliko su sigurne države koje špijuniraju?","category":"technology","date":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"FBI istražuje provalu u svoje sustave za [prisluškivanje i nadzor](https://www.","execSummary":"The FBI's surveillance systems breach isn't just a security failure—it's a wake-up call for enterprises and governments relying on 'unhackable' tools. This article cuts through the hype to ask: if state-level actors can't protect their own spyware, what does that mean for commercial security promises and user trust?","keyPoints":["FBI istražuje provaljen sustav prisluškivanja i nadzora","Nejasno koliko je osjetljivih podataka ugroženo","Što to znači za privatnost i sigurnost korisnika?"],"source":{"name":"TechCrunch","url":"https://techcrunch.com/2026/03/05/fbi-investigating-hack-on-its-wiretap-and-surveillance-systems-report/"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/fbis-surveillance-hack-more-than-just-a-security-s/main.jpg","alt":"FBI-ov hack: Koliko su sigurne države koje špijuniraju?"},"subtitle":"Kada špijuniraš druge, tko čuva tvoje podatke?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/fbis-surveillance-hack-more-than-just-a-security-s/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Kada špijuniraš druge, tko čuva tvoje podatke?"},"tags":["Cybersecurity","Data Privacy","FBI","Surveillance"],"geo":{"name":"San Francisco, US","lat":37.7749,"lon":-122.4194,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$12","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-22-instagrams-encryption-retreat-why-vpns-wont-fix-th","title":"Instagram gubi šifru – VPN postaje nužan trošak?","category":"technology","date":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Ako ste vjerovali da su vaše privatne poruke na Instagramu zaista *privatne*, Meta vas upravo razuvjerila.","execSummary":"Meta’s removal of end-to-end encryption on Instagram shifts privacy from a default to a premium feature, forcing users to rely on VPNs or accept exposure. This move highlights the growing divide between platform convenience and user security—with real costs for businesses and individuals who assumed their DMs were protected.","keyPoints":["Meta ukida krajnju šifru na Instagramu bez jasnog datuma","VPN-ovi postaju minimalna zaštita, a ne samo alati za geoblock","Korisnici i konkurencija reagiraju: tko će platiti cijenu privatnosti?"],"source":{"name":"PCGamesN","url":"https://www.pcgamesn.com/vpn/instagram-privacy"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/instagrams-encryption-retreat-why-vpns-wont-fix-th/main.jpg","alt":"Instagram gubi šifru – VPN postaje nužan trošak?"},"subtitle":"Što znači kad platforma prestane štititi vaše poruke – i što s tim sad?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/instagrams-encryption-retreat-why-vpns-wont-fix-th/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Što znači kad platforma prestane štititi vaše poruke – i što s tim sad?"},"tags":["Instagram","VPN","Data Privacy"],"geo":{"name":"San Francisco, US","lat":37.7749,"lon":-122.4194,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$13","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-22-meta-s-smart-glasses-capture-more-than-moments","title":"Metaove naočale snimaju WC – tko je kriv za ovaj propust?","category":"technology","date":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Kad je Meta prije godinu dana predstavio svoje smart naočale u suradnji s Ray-Banom, obećao je „budućnost koja oslobađa ruke i povezuje ljude“.","execSummary":"Meta’s Ray-Ban smart glasses privacy breach isn’t just another scandal—it’s a systemic failure exposing how *wearable* tech prioritizes data collection over user trust. The real tension lies in whether this will trigger meaningful regulation or just become another forgotten footnote in Big Tech’s playbook.","keyPoints":["Radnici gledaju intimne snimke s Meta-RayBan naočala","Privatnost opet u pitanju: marketing vs. stvarna upotreba","Regulatorna bujica ili samo još jedan skandal bez posljedica?"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/meta-s-smart-glasses-capture-more-than-moments/main.jpg","alt":"Metaove naočale snimaju WC – tko je kriv za ovaj propust?"},"subtitle":"Kada pametna tehnologija postane preglup instrument nadzora","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/meta-s-smart-glasses-capture-more-than-moments/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Kada pametna tehnologija postane preglup instrument nadzora"},"tags":["Meta","Smart Glasses","Surveillance"],"geo":{"name":"Menl