romiču fiksne godišnje naknade za vlasnike električnih vozila — 200 do 250 dolara, iznos koji je dva do tri puta veći od prosječnog saveznog poreza na gorivo koji plaćaju vlasnici vozila s klasičnim motorima.","execSummary":"U.S. lawmakers are pushing flat EV fees (200–250 USD/year) that disproportionately target early adopters, ignoring health and infrastructure savings EVs provide. The move risks slowing adoption just as China dominates the battery market—raising questions about whether this is fair cost-sharing or a penalty on progress.","keyPoints":["Godišnja naknada od 200–250$ za EV — tri puta više od benzinca","10% prodaje, ali infrastruktura se financira po starim pravilima","Zdravlje, okoliš i sigurnost — benefiti koje naknade ignoriraju"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/ev-owners-face-250-feeswhile-gas-drivers-pay-a-fra/main.jpg","alt":"EV vlasnici plaćaju 3x više: tko zapravo gradi ceste?"},"subtitle":"Kad matematička jednadžba ne stane: 1,4 milijuna EV-a u SAD-u subvencionira ceste za sve, a plaća kao kazneni porez","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/ev-owners-face-250-feeswhile-gas-drivers-pay-a-fra/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Kad matematička jednadžba ne stane: 1,4 milijuna EV-a u SAD-u subvencionira ceste za sve, a plaća kao kazneni porez"},"tags":["Electric Vehicles","Road Infrastructure","Subsidies","Transportation Policy"],"geo":{"name":"Sjedinjene Američke Države (SAD), USA","lat":37.09024,"lon":-95.712891,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$16","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-19-nand-prices-spike-50-overnightwho-pays-the-real-co","title":"NAND čipovi skočili 50% preko noći – tko će platiti račun?","category":"technology","date":"2026-03-19T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-19T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Ako ste mislili da su cijene pohrane već dosegle dno, pogriješili ste.","execSummary":"Phison’s report of a 50% overnight NAND price surge isn’t just a supply-chain blip—it’s a structural warning. The shift exposes vulnerabilities in storage markets, with immediate cost hikes for SSDs and long-term risks for non-enterprise buyers. The real question: Is this a temporary crunch or the new normal for memory pricing?","keyPoints":["Cijene NAND čipova porasle za 50% u jednoj noći","Phison ubrzano povećava zalihe za poslovne kupce","Opasnost od lančanog učinka na SSD tržište i krajnje korisnike"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/nand-prices-spike-50-overnightwho-pays-the-real-co/main.jpg","alt":"NAND čipovi skočili 50% preko noći – tko će platiti račun?"},"subtitle":"Kada skok cijena nije samo brojka, nego upozorenje o nedostatku koji može promijeniti igru","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/nand-prices-spike-50-overnightwho-pays-the-real-co/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Kada skok cijena nije samo brojka, nego upozorenje o nedostatku koji može promijeniti igru"},"tags":["NAND chips","semiconductor shortage","price surge"],"geo":{"name":"Hsinchu, Taiwan","lat":24.8138,"lon":120.9675,"countryCode":"XX"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$17","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-17-ternary-cpus-why-binarys-reign-might-finally-be-cr","title":"Ternarni procesor: Hoće li trojka zamijeniti binarnu logiku?","category":"technology","date":"2026-03-17T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-17T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Većina inženjera bi se nasmijala na pitanje: jesu li svi procesori binarni.","execSummary":"A ternary RISC processor implemented on FPGA challenges binary dominance, but its real-world impact depends on ecosystem adoption. The article dissects practical hurdles—tooling gaps, cost trade-offs, and niche use cases—while questioning whether this is a meaningful shift or an academic curiosity.","keyPoints":["Trojni RISC procesor radi na FPGA platformi","Binarnu dominaciju izaziva nebinarni pristup","Potencijal za efikasniju obradu — ali za koga?"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/ternary-cpus-why-binarys-reign-mi